  (kiesel)
  
Bugfixes
~~~~~~~~~
- Fixed duplicate redirect in scriptlet API when used with sessions
  (friebe)
- Fix remote.protocol.Serializer bug in best mapping finding
  algorithm
  (Frank Kleine, kiesel)
- Fix deserialization of objects of XP types
  (kiesel)
